lass=\"s2\"><a href=\"mailto:elatimerlo@ivsn.org\">elatimerlo@ivsn.org</a> </span></span>or (650) 685-5880 ext. 115.\r\n<h2>Employers who make matching gifts to InnVision Shelter Network</h2>\r\nAbbott Laboratories\r\nAdobe Systems Incorporated\r\nAetna Foundation\r\nAgilent Technologies\r\nAllstate\r\nAMD\r\nAmerica\'s Charities\r\nApple\r\nAT&amp;T\r\nBank of America\r\nBank of The West\r\nBill &amp; Melinda Gates Foundation\r\nCharles Schwab\r\nChevron\r\nThe Clorox Company\r\nDavid and Lucile Packard Foundation\r\nDolby\r\nElectronic Arts\r\nExpedia Inc.\r\nFranklin Templeton Investments\r\nGap Inc.\r\nGlobal Impact\r\nGoogle\r\nHewlett-Packard\r\nIBM\r\nJuniper Networks\r\nThe Henry J. Kaiser Family Foundation\r\nKaiser Permanente\r\nMcGraw-Hill\r\nMerck\r\nMerrill Lynch &amp; Co.\r\nMicrosoft\r\nMorgan Stanley\r\nOracle Corporation\r\nOrange County\'s United Way\r\nPG&amp;E Corporation\r\nRaychem\r\nSandisk Corporation\r\nSun Microsystems\r\nSymantec\r\nTektronix\r\nTyco\r\nUnion Bank of California\r\nUnited Airlines\r\nUnited Business Media, LLC\r\nTarget\r\nVarian\r\nVisa\r\nVMWare\r\nWells Fargo','Employee Matching','','publish','closed','open','','employee-matching','','','2015-05-21 20:49:56','2015-05-22 03:49:56','',207,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/?page_id=295',70,'page','',0),(301,2,'2013-10-08 03:46:26','2013-10-08 03:46:26',' ','','','publish','closed','open','','301','','','2014-08-26 14:46:36','2014-08-26 21:46:36','',207,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/?p=301',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(303,2,'2013-10-08 04:22:08','2013-10-08 04:22:08','<h1><img class=\"alignright wp-image-394\" src=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/donate_holiday_dinner_basket-320x426.jpg\" alt=\"donate_holiday_dinner_basket\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" />Thanksgiving and Holiday Dinner Baskets</h1>\r\nThere’s nothing like a delicious feast to bring a family together for the holidays! To participate by donating a Holiday Dinner Basket, email Jessie Ellington at <a href=\"mailto:jellington@ivsn.org\">jellington@ivsn.org</a>.\r\n\r\n<strong>Total Estimated Cost of Dinner Basket: $40 (including $10-15 gift card)</strong>\r\n\r\nThank you!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Holiday Dinner Baskets','','publish','closed','open','','holiday-dinner-baskets','','','2015-09-15 11:52:07','2015-09-15 18:52:07','',216,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/?page_id=303',68,'page','',0),(304,2,'2013-10-08 04:23:21','2013-10-08 04:23:21',' ','','','publish','closed','open','','304','','','2014-08-26 14:46:36','2014-08-26 21:46:36','',216,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/?p=304',13,'nav_menu_item','',0),(329,2,'2013-10-08 09:31:43','2013-10-08 09:31:43','<h1>Relief Shelter Worker</h1>\r\n<b>Location:</b> Multiple Locations Available San Jose, Daly City, Palo Alto, Redwood City, San Mateo\r\n\r\n<b>Program Summary: </b>InnVision Shelter Network (IVSN) is one of the largest and most effective providers of shelter/housing and supportive services across Silicon Valley and the San Francisco Peninsula, serving thousands of homeless families and individuals annually on their path back to self-sufficiency. The Shelter Worker, Relief position is responsible for the safety and well-being of the program participants.\r\n\r\nThis is a part-time position requiring mostly weekends, holidays, swing and/or graveyard shifts.\r\n<h2> Primary Responsibilities</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Welcome new participants and supervise move-ins and outs.</li>\r\n	<li>Responsible for the \"Daily Log Book\" and monitoring of client activities within the shelter to maintain a</li>\r\n	<li>safe and supportive atmosphere.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure client adherence to program rules, especially related to behaviors that are disruptive or unsafe.</li>\r\n	<li>Respond appropriately to shelter emergencies.</li>\r\n	<li>Administrative duties including mail, telephone coverage, supply inventory and donations.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Qualifications</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Demonstrated experience working in some type of community supportive or social services</li>\r\n	<li>environment, preferably with an organization that addresses homelessness.</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to work BOTH independently and as part of a team are a MUST.</li>\r\n	<li>Fluency in Spanish extremely helpful.</li>\r\n	<li>A clean driving record and computer skills are required.</li>\r\n	<li>Administrative and/or customer service experience preferred.</li>\r\n	<li>Must be able to \"think on your feet\" and apply good common-sense judgment.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTo apply, please e-mail a resume and brief cover letter to: <a href=\"mailto:jobs@ivsn.org\">jobs@ivsn.org</a>. Include the job title in the subject line. Please send as attachments!\r\n\r\n<em>No phone calls, please. Thank you in advance for your interest, time, and effort. InnVision Shelter Network is an Equal Opportunity Employer (EOE). Applicants are considered for employment without regard to age, race, color, religion, sex, national origin, sexual orientation, gender identity and gender expression, disability or veteran status.</em>','Relief Shelter Worker','','publish','closed','open','','shelter-worker-relief','','','2014-01-22 16:26:29','2014-01-23 00:26:29','',251,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/?page_id=329',65,'page','',0),(333,2,'2013-10-08 10:00:41','2013-10-08 10:00:41','','karae-sig','','inherit','closed','open','','karae-sig','','','2014-11-18 18:52:56','2014-11-19 02:52:56','',1071,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/karae-sig.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(335,2,'2013-10-08 10:31:32','2013-10-08 10:31:32','','2013-Homeless-Census-and-Survey-San-Mateo-County','','inherit','closed','open','','2013-homeless-census-and-survey-san-mateo-county','','','2013-10-08 10:31:32','2013-10-08 10:31:32','',0,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2013-Homeless-Census-and-Survey-San-Mateo-County.pdf',0,'attachment','application/pdf',0),(336,2,'2013-10-08 10:31:45','2013-10-08 10:31:45','','2013-Santa-Clara-County-Homeless-Census-and-Survey','','inherit','closed','open','','2013-santa-clara-county-homeless-census-and-survey','','','2013-10-08 10:31:45','2013-10-08 10:31:45','',0,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2013-Santa-Clara-County-Homeless-Census-and-Survey.pdf',0,'attachment','application/pdf',0),(338,2,'2013-10-08 11:17:52','2013-10-08 11:17:52','','Youth-CORE-Flyer-8.5x11','','inherit','closed','open','','youth-core-flyer-8-5x11','','','2013-10-08 11:17:52','2013-10-08 11:17:52','',0,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Youth-CORE-Flyer-8.5x11.pdf',0,'attachment','application/pdf',0),(347,2,'2013-10-08 12:20:43','2013-10-08 12:20:43','','Lynne Twist','','inherit','closed','open','','lynnetwist_sm','','','2013-10-08 12:20:43','2013-10-08 12:20:43','',49,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/lynneTwist_sm.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(349,2,'2013-10-08 14:27:05','2013-10-08 14:27:05','','Shellye Archambeau','Shellye Archambeau, CEO of MetricStream','inherit','closed','open','','shellyearchambeau_sm','','','2013-10-08 14:27:05','2013-10-08 14:27:05','',0,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/ShellyeArchambeau_sm.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(353,2,'2013-10-08 14:48:05','2013-10-08 14:48:05','','IVSNlogo','','inherit','closed','open','','ivsnlogo','','','2013-10-08 14:48:05','2013-10-08 14:48:05','',180,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/IVSNlogo.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(355,2,'2013-10-08 15:00:43','2013-10-08 15:00:43','<h1><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-412\" alt=\"gethelp_homeless_mother_kissing_cheek\" src=\"http://www.ivsn.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/gethelp_homeless_mother_kissing_cheek-320x214.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"214\" />Get Involved</h1>\r\nThrough donating, volunteering, and more, you can support the homeless families and individuals at InnVision Shelter Network.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Donate</h2>\r\n[one_half]<a title=\"Donate\" href=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/donate/\"><strong>Make a Financial Contribution</strong></a>\r\n\r\nIVSN’s services are only made possible through generous financial support from the community year-round. Your gift ensures that we may continue to provide housing and supportive services to thousands of homeless children and adults.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/donate/\"><strong>Give in Honor of a Loved One</strong></a>\r\n\r\nMake a financial donation to IVSN in honor or in memory of a friend or family member. We will mail the honoree a special acknowledgement card with artwork drawn by children at our shelters.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Employee Matching\" href=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/donate/corporate-partners/employee-matching/\"><b>Ask Your Employer to Match</b></a>\r\n\r\nMany companies offer matching donations to double the impact of your gift. Some employers will even match your volunteer time with a charitable donation!\r\n\r\n[/one_half][one_half_last]<a title=\"Party With A Purpose\" href=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/donate/party-with-a-purpose/\"><b>Host a Party With a Purpose</b></a>\r\n\r\nIn lieu of presents, ask your friends, family, or coworkers to bring a donation to your next social gathering. Most needed items include financial donations, gift certificates, linens, cooking supplies, dishware, and new socks and undergarments.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Individual Giving\" href=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/donate/individual-giving/\"><b>Include IVSN in Your Estate Plan</b></a>\r\n\r\nA charitable bequest, living trust, or gift in your will has a lasting impact on our work to end homelessness. Contact us to learn more about the many ways to arrange a planned gift to IVSN.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Donate Items\" href=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/donate/donate-items/\"><b>Donate a Vehicle, Stock, or Property</b></a>\r\n\r\nThere are many ways to donate beyond traditional financial giving. Contact us and we’ll be happy to discuss creative giving options that offer the greatest impact toward IVSN’s mission and your philanthropic goals.\r\n[/one_half_last]\r\n<div align=\"center\"><hr align=\"center\" noshade=\"noshade\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" /></div>\r\n<h2>Volunteer</h2>\r\n[one_half]<a title=\"For Individuals\" href=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/volunteer/for-individuals/\"><b>Give Time and Skills</b></a>\r\n\r\nEvery person has volunteer skills to offer, such as teaching workshops, tutoring students, organizing donations, preparing meals, and much more. Volunteer your time today!\r\n\r\n<a title=\"For Companies\" href=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/volunteer/for-companies/\"><strong>Team Build with your Company</strong></a>\r\n\r\nEngage your coworkers in team-building volunteer projects that make a difference for people in need.\r\n[/one_half][one_half_last]<a title=\"For Groups\" href=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/volunteer/for-groups/\"><b>Organize a Group Project</b></a>\r\n\r\nVolunteer with your friends or colleagues in a done-in-a-day project, such as serving meals, hosting a shelter event, or beautifying our facilities. Group projects offer the opportunity to get out and give back with a team of volunteers.[/one_half_last]\r\n<div align=\"center\"><hr align=\"center\" noshade=\"noshade\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" /></div>\r\n<h2>Partner</h2>\r\n[one_half]<a href=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/connect/get-involved/landlord-leader/\"><strong>Become a Landlord Leader</strong></a>\r\n\r\nHelp IVSN by renting your apartment to one of our clients. Give a second chance to a hard-working person who has proven they are committed to regaining self-sufficiency.\r\n\r\n[/one_half][one_half_last]<a title=\"Hire Jobseekers\" href=\"http://www.ivsn.org/connect/get-involved/hire-jobseekers/\"><strong>Hire a Jobseeker</strong></a>\r\n\r\nPartner with IVSN to hire motivated, qualified employees working to build brighter futures.[/one_half_last]\r\n<div align=\"center\"><hr align=\"center\" noshade=\"noshade\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" /></div>\r\n<h2>Connect</h2>\r\n[one_half]<a href=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/connect/take-a-tour/\"><strong>Take a Shelter Tour</strong></a>\r\n\r\nThere is nothing like the experience of visiting a shelter. Schedule a tour and see the impact of our services first-hand. You won’t regret taking the time to learn more about homelessness and nonprofit services in your community.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/news-events/news/\"><strong>Read Our Blog</strong></a>\r\n\r\nRead about the latest news, events, and inspiration stories at InnVision Shelter Network. There is so much happening all the time, and we look forward to sharing it with you!\r\n\r\n[/one_half][one_half_last]<a title=\"Newsletters\" href=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/news-events/newsletters/\"><strong>Sign Up for Our E-Newsletter</strong></a>\r\n\r\nStay up-to-date on the latest happenings at InnVision Shelter Network.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/connect/social-media/\"><strong>Join the Conversation on Social Media</strong></a>\r\n\r\nTell your friends, family, and colleagues about IVSN’s work in the community, so that we may continue to expand our network of support. Connect with us on Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn, or YouTube.[/one_half_last]','Get Involved','','publish','closed','open','','get-involved','','','2013-11-01 16:42:19','2013-11-01 23:42:19','',9,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/?page_id=355',64,'page','',0),(357,2,'2013-10-08 17:12:37','2013-10-08 17:12:37','','Volunteer-Flyer','','inherit','closed','open','','volunteer-flyer','','','2013-10-08 17:12:37','2013-10-08 17:12:37','',18,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Volunteer-Flyer.pdf',0,'attachment','application/pdf',0),(358,2,'2013-10-08 17:26:49','2013-10-08 17:26:49',' ','','','publish','closed','open','','358','','','2013-10-08 20:18:06','2013-10-08 20:18:06','',0,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/?p=358',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(359,2,'2013-10-08 17:30:32','2013-10-08 17:30:32',' ','','','publish','closed','open','','359','','','2013-10-08 20:18:09','2013-10-08 20: