losed','open','','make_a_financial_donation','','','2013-10-08 18:24:45','2013-10-08 18:24:45','',216,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/make_a_financial_donation.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(368,2,'2013-10-08 18:24:46','2013-10-08 18:24:46','','sign_up_now','','inherit','closed','open','','sign_up_now','','','2013-10-08 18:24:46','2013-10-08 18:24:46','',216,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/sign_up_now.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(370,2,'2013-10-08 18:29:50','2013-10-08 18:29:50','','sign_up_to_volunteer','','inherit','closed','open','','sign_up_to_volunteer','','','2013-10-08 18:29:50','2013-10-08 18:29:50','',184,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/sign_up_to_volunteer.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(371,2,'2013-10-08 18:41:47','2013-10-08 18:41:47',' ','','','publish','closed','open','','371','','','2014-07-08 15:22:01','2014-07-08 22:22:01','',6,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/?p=371',26,'nav_menu_item','',0),(373,2,'2013-10-08 18:47:10','2013-10-08 18:47:10','<h1>Become a Landlord Leader</h1>\r\nHelp IVSN by renting your apartment to one of our clients. Give a second chance to a hard-working person who has proven they are committed to regaining self-sufficiency.\r\n<h2>Give Back to Your Community</h2>\r\nAs active members of the community, we are responsible for helping those in need and making a difference in their lives. By renting to an IVSN client, you can give someone a second chance to become self-sufficient.\r\n<h2>Find A Tenant with Professional Support</h2>\r\nIVSN clients are paired with a specialized case manager to keep them on track and train them on housing readiness. As a landlord, you will be connected with your tenant’s case manager to contact directly and partner together in promoting your tenant’s housing success.\r\n<h2>Contact</h2>\r\nContact Erica Hoxie, Landlord Outreach Associate\r\n(650) 999-1376, <a href=\"mailto:ehoxie@ivsn.org\">ehoxie@ivsn.org</a>','Landlord Leader','','publish','closed','open','','landlord-leader','','','2013-10-08 18:47:10','2013-10-08 18:47:10','',355,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/?page_id=373',63,'page','',0),(374,2,'2013-10-08 18:50:03','2013-10-08 18:50:03','<h1><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-417\" alt=\"services_homeless_man_computer\" src=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/services_homeless_man_computer-320x180.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"180\" />Employers: Hire Jobseekers to Better Our Community</h1>\r\nInnVision Shelter Network (IVSN) is partnering with employers of all sizes and industries to hire motivated, qualified employees working to build brighter futures.\r\n\r\nClients at InnVision Shelter Network are hard-working and driven to effectively change their lives for the better. You can give them a second chance and make a positive impact in our community.\r\n<h2>Give Back to Your Community</h2>\r\nAs active members of the community, we are responsible for helping those in need and making a difference in their lives. By hiring an IVSN client, you can give someone a second chance to become self-sufficient.\r\n<h2>Hire an Employee with Professional Support</h2>\r\nIVSN clients are paired with a specialized case manager to keep them on track and train them on workplace preparedness. As an employer, you will be connected with your employee’s case manager to contact directly and partner together in promoting your employee’s success.\r\n<h2>Make a Financial Investment</h2>\r\nEmployers may receive a Work Opportunity Tax Credit for up to $2,400 per employee. In addition, your investment in your employee’s success saves valuable taxpayer dollars otherwise spent on the criminal justice system.\r\n<h2>Be a Visible Philanthropic Partner</h2>\r\nWhen you hire an IVSN client, you will be given a “Proud Partner” plaque to display in your store/office. We will also include your logo on our website as an Employer Partner. Show your employees, customers, and stakeholders that you are actively involved in our community.\r\n<h2>Contact</h2>\r\nSebastain Gould, Realignment Job Development Specialist\r\n<a href=\"mailto:sgould@ivsn.org\">sgould@ivsn.org</a>,  (650) 248-3510','Hire Jobseekers','','publish','closed','open','','hire-jobseekers','','','2013-10-14 23:48:47','2013-10-14 23:48:47','',355,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/?page_id=374',62,'page','',0),(375,2,'2013-10-08 18:51:23','2013-10-08 18:51:23','<h1><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-378\" src=\"http://ivsn.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/connect_family_haven_sign-320x214.jpg\" alt=\"connect_family_haven_sign\" width=\"320\" height=\"214\" />Take a Tour</h1>\r\nThere is nothing like the experience of visiting a shelter. Schedule a tour and see the impact of our services first-hand. You won’t regret taking the time to learn more about homelessness and nonprofit services in your community.\r\n<h2>Contact Us for a Tour!</h2>\r\nPlease contact <span style=\"color: #000000;\">Marissa Robbins</span> at either (650) 685-5880 ext. 156 or <a href=\"mailto:tours@ivsn.org\" target=\"_blank\">tours@ivsn.org</a>','Take a Tour','','publish','closed','open','','take-a-tour','','','2014-11-19 11:11:20','2014-11-19 19:11:20','',9,'http://ivsn.wpengine.com/?page_id=375',61,'page','',0),(376,2,'2013-10-08 18:52:09','2013-10-08 18:52:09','<h1>Connect on Social Media</h1>\r\nShare with your friends, family, and colleagues about IVSN’s work in the community. Tell your network why you care about effective solutions to homelessness.\r\n<h2>Join the conversation with IVSN on social media!</h2>\r\n<div class=\"volunteer-buttons\"><a title=\"Facebook\" href=\" https://www.facebook.com/InnVisionShelterNetwork\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-199 alignnone\" alt=\"facebook\" src=\" http://ivsn.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/facebook_button.png\" width=\"161\" height=\"51\" /></a> <a title=\"Twitter\" href=\" https://twitter.com/InnVisShelter\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\