 loved one. We will mail the honoree a special holiday card with artwork created by children at our shelters. <a href=\"https://14345.thankyou4caring.org/sslpage.aspx?pid=392\">Donate Now</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Host a “Party with a Purpose”</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">In lieu of traditional presents, ask your friends, family, or coworkers to bring a cash gift for neighbors in need to your next holiday gathering.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Adopt-a-Household</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">Every IVSN client participating in housing services will receive two holiday gift wishes. You can make these wishes come true by “adopting” a family or individual. Purchase a single gift, or shop for a whole family!</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Donate a Thanksgiving or Holiday Dinner Basket</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">With your donation of gift cards and/or dinner baskets, every family in IVSN programs will be able to enjoy a holiday meal together.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Host a Gift Drive</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">Ask your friends, family or co-workers to bring gifts for homeless neighbors. Most needed items include gift cards ($30 value), linens, new socks and undergarments.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Volunteer</h2>\r\n<strong>Plan a Holiday Party at a Shelter</strong>\r\n\r\nHost a party or a “Cookies &amp; Carols” event at one of our shelter residences with your friends, coworkers, or volunteer group. A festive celebration makes the holidays bright and memorable for our clients.  <a href=\"http://www.formsite.com/shelternetwork/form43/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Provide and Serve Holiday Meals</strong>\r\n\r\nGather a group of your friends or coworkers to provide and serve a special meal to our residents. On Thanksgiving Day, Christmas Eve, Christmas Day, New Year’s Eve, or New Year’s Day—in addition to weekends (Saturdays and Sundays) throughout the year.<a href=\"https://www.formsite.com/shelternetwork/form73/index.html?1444862360261\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n</a>\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Meal Provider Volunteer Manual\" href=\"http://www.ivsn.org/volunteer/meal-programs/\">Click here to find availability and sign up to provide a meal.</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Decorate a Shelter</strong>\r\n\r\nVolunteer with a group of your friends or colleagues to bring in decorations and turn a shelter into a winter wonderland. <a href=\"http://www.formsite.com/shelternetwork/form43/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n</a>','Plan Your 2015 Holiday Giving and Volunteering!','','inherit','closed','closed','','1577-autosave-v1','','','2015-11-04 14:39:55','2015-11-04 22:39:55','',1577,'http://www.ivsn.org/1577-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1581,23,'2015-10-27 15:07:55','2015-10-27 22:07:55','','Carolands-Holiday-Party_Children','','inherit','closed','closed','','carolands-holiday-party_children-2','','','2015-10-27 15:07:55','2015-10-27 22:07:55','',1577,'http://www.ivsn.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Carolands-Holiday-Party_Children.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1582,23,'2015-10-27 15:20:57','2015-10-27 22:20:57','','Holiday website image 2015_revised','','inherit','closed','closed','','holiday-website-image-2015_revised','','','2015-10-27 15:20:57','2015-10-27 22:20:57','',1577,'http://www.ivsn.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Holiday-website-image-2015_revised.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1584,12,'2015-11-02 12:28:19','2015-11-02 20:28:19','','NextGen Advisory Board','','inherit','closed','closed','','img_6231-edit','','','2015-11-02 12:28:41','2015-11-02 20:28:41','',665,'http://www.ivsn.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/IMG_6231-edit.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1585,12,'2015-11-02 15:10:57','2015-11-02 23:10:57','','_D4F2683','','inherit','closed','closed','','_d4f2683','','','2015-11-02 15:10:57','2015-11-02 23:10:57','',665,'http://www.ivsn.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/D4F2683.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1586,12,'2015-11-02 15:12:10','2015-11-02 23:12:10','','Marshall Fisher',